    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know if there's anything left to reconnect to. it's like the body is just staying alive out of habit, but the person who was supposed to live this life is just... finished. it feels more like a funeral that never ends. like i'm just waiting for the rest of me to catch up to the part that already died.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
